  "depth": 3,
  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Manual Entry of Basis Spread Values</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page concept  - topic-topic concept-concept \" id=\"loioacbf00518cee4d5ce10000000a44176d\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Manual Entry of Basis Spread Values</h1><div class=\"body conbody\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2><p class=\"p\">You use this function to enter basis spread values manually in the market data tables. A basis spread value always relates to a basis spread ID, a quotation type, and a rate date. You can enter positive as well as negative basis spread values.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Prerequisites\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Prerequisites</h2><p class=\"p\">You need to have created the basis spreads in Customizing for <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span> under <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basic Functions</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Market Data Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Master Data</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basis Spreads</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Define Basis Spreads</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Activities\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Activities</h2><ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Call the function in the SAP Easy Access menu for <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span> under <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basic Functions</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Market Data Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Manual Market Data Entry</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basis Spreads</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Enter Basis Spreads</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> (transaction <span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">RMBSM</span>) or in Customizing under <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basic Functions</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Market Data Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Manual Market Data Entry</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basis Spreads</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Enter Basis Spreads</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Display</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Choose</span> to call up the display/change mode for the market data table for the basis spread values.\n</p><aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<p class=\"p\">To restrict the number of basis spread values in the display, you can use the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basis Spread ID</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Quotation Type</span>, and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Rate Date</span> fields.\n</p></aside><p class=\"p\">By choosing <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loio0e0fe47e342f4c8f903ff399c0993c3c_LowRes.png\" alt=\"Display <-&gt; Change\" title=\"Display <-&gt; Change\">, you can switch between the display and change modes.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">In the change mode, you can enter new basis spread values or change existing ones.\n</p><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Entering Basis Spread Values</span>\n</p><ol class=\"ol\" type=\"a\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">New Entries</span>.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Enter a basis spread ID in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basis Spread ID</span> field and a quotation type in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Quotation Type</span> field.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Enter the quotation date in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Quotation Date</span> field.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Enter the basis spread values in basis points, where one basis point corresponds to a hundredth of a percentage point.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">To enter an additional basis spread value, choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loioa58193d89b1c48ef84276dcbe7cf0a95_LowRes.png\" alt=\"New Input Line\" title=\"New Input Line\">.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">If you have entered a line incorrectly, select the line and choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loiod91d72047c214e2f84269618b890d2b2_LowRes.png\" alt=\"Delete\" title=\"Delete\">.\n</p></li></ol><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Changing Basis Spread Values</span>\n</p><p class=\"p\">You can change or delete existing basis spread values.\n</p><p class=\"p\">To delete a value, select the line and choose <img class=\"inline\" src=\"loiod91d72047c214e2f84269618b890d2b2_LowRes.png\" alt=\"Delete\" title=\"Delete\">.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Save your entries.\n</p></li></ol>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}